OL,5, The boss of the Post Office Nick Read  
OL,6, has been cleared of misconduct         
OL,7, allegations after an investigation on  
OL,8, behalf of the organisation.            
OL,10,FThe Post Office said Mr Read has "the  
OL,11,Ffull and united backing of the board"  
OL,12,Fto continue in his role following the  
OL,13,Finvestigation by an external barrister.
OL,15,FMr Read also has the confidence of the 
OL,16,Fgovernment, a spokesperson said.       
OL,18,FThe investigation into Mr Read's       
OL,19,Fconduct had been revealed by former    
OL,20,FPost Office chairman Henry Staunton.   
